                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Haven't done much JC in the last few weeks, and I log in to make a little money at my favorite vendor...well, I go to sell my newly-made JC items and find that they seem to sell for roughly ten percent less than they used to.
<br />

<br />
Bear in mind I have CHA maxed (255), even tried Collaboration to improve the selling price...still, silver diamond wedding rings now sell for 200 plat 5 gold instead of the 219 plat and change they used to sell for.  I tried it with silver ruby veils and the same thing occurred, though I forget the actual prices now.
<br />

<br />
Did I miss something in a patch message?
<br />

<br />
If so, /rude Sony BIG time...if not, FIX your dang game!</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Grimbul Garnet
<br />
Intrepid Gnomey Enchanter
<br />
Mithaniel Marr</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
